IMAPAccount alocybe
Host imap.gmail.com
User alocybe@gmail.com
PassCmd "0m alocybe"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile ~/.guix-profile/etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore alocybe-remote
Account alocybe

MaildirStore alocybe-local
Subfolders verbatim
Path /data/mail/alocybe/
Inbox /data/mail/alocybe/inbox

Channel alocybe-inbox
Master :alocybe-remote:
Slave :alocybe-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel alocybe-sent
Master :alocybe-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :alocybe-local:sent

Channel alocybe-drafts
Master :alocybe-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :alocybe-local:drafts

Channel alocybe-spam
Master :alocybe-remote:"[Gmail]/Spam"
Slave :alocybe-local:spam

Channel alocybe-trash
Master :alocybe-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :alocybe-local:trash

Create Both
Expunge None
SyncState *

Group alocybe
Channel alocybe-inbox
Channel alocybe-sent
Channel alocybe-drafts
Channel alocybe-spam
Channel alocybe-trash

